      "title_en": "Adj. + 吗？ — asking about a state",
      "desc_en": "By adding \"吗\" after an adjective, you can ask about a state. The answer is the adjective itself.",
      "formula_en": "Adj. + 吗？ → Adj. / 不 + Adj.",
